<p>The <code>@key</code> property returns the current array key.</p>

<h2>Associative Array Keys</h2>
<pre>{open}config{close}
  {open}@key{close}: {open}$config{close}
{open}/config{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<div>
{config}
  {@key}: {$config}<br>
{/config}
</div>

<h2>Numeric Array Keys</h2>
<pre>{open}colors{close}
  Key [{open}@key{close}] = {open}$colors{close}
{open}/colors{close}</pre>

<p>Result:</p>
<div>
{colors}
  Key [{@key}] = {$colors}<br>
{/colors}
</div>
